      "responseEnvelope": "SuccessEnvelope",
      "notes": "Requires an admin_key with instances:destroy or admin:*. Returns operationStatus=accepted. TUI should remove the item from active lists after success and may keep detail views able to show status=destroyed. Provider disconnect is attempted through the provider-runtime bridge when configured; raw provider/session payloads are not exposed."
    },
